<h1>User Interface</h1>
<p>This documentation walks you through the key elements of the Fluent Forms user interface, including the dashboard, form list, and builder screen.</p>
<img src="https://docs.fluentforms.com/images/getting-started/install-fluent-forms/Fluent-Form-install-01-scaled.webp" alt="Fluent Forms Dashboard" class="docs-img">
<h2>Dashboard</h2>
<p>The dashboard is Fluent Forms' main control center. From here, you can view an overview of all your forms, track recent submissions, view analytics, and manage everything in one place.</p>
<h2>Top Menu</h2>
<p>At the top, you'll find menu items like Entries, Payments, Global Settings, Tools, Integrations, and Support, giving quick access to all major sections.</p>